data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom beauty is ready to welcome you with open arms. Boasting over 2300 square feet of pure comfort and elegance, this home is move-in ready and waiting for your personal touch.  Situated in a fantastic location, convenience will be your new best friend. Imagine being just minutes away from shopping centers, mouthwatering restaurants, thrilling theme parks, major roads, and even the airport. Say goodbye to long commutes and hello to a stress-free lifestyle.    As you step inside, be prepared to be amazed. The lower level features gorgeous hard flooring throughout, adding a touch of sophistication to every room. The master bedroom, conveniently located on this floor, offers ultimate privacy and tranquility. Prepare to be spoiled in your oversized bathroom and relax in your spacious walk-in closet that dreams are made of.    On the second floor, you'll find brand new plush carpeting that will make you want to sink your toes in every step of the way. With the remaining three bedrooms, there's space for everyone to enjoy their own little haven.    Entertaining friends and family is a breeze in this home. The high ceilings create an airy and open atmosphere that will leave a lasting impression on guests. Step out onto the screened-in back porch and enjoy the peaceful outdoors without the hassle of pesky bugs. The fenced yard offers privacy and safety, making it the perfect spot for family and pets to run and play.    The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a chef's dream come true. Marvel at the beautiful granite counters while whipping up culinary delights. With stainless steel appliances, an abundance of cabinet space, and a layout designed for efficiency, preparing meals will be an absolute joy.    This home QUALIFIES to assume the mortgage at at 3.75%!!!!!     Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this remarkable house your forever home. Schedule your private showing and let yourself fall in love with the endless possibilities this home has to offer. Your dream awaits!
